author: KXAS-TV (NBC5)
title: Watch: Tractor trailer crash shuts down southbound I-35E in northwest Dallas
text:
The southbound lanes of Interstate 35E at Royal Lane are closed in northwest Dallas after a crash, KXAS-TV (NBC5) reports . 
Police say a tractor trailer collided with at least two other vehicles around 4 p.m. Tuesday. It appears one of those vehicles caught fire. 
It is unclear whether anyone has been injured. 
Dallas Fire-Rescue and police are on the scene.
